                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18050424-22-off124 t18050424-22-cd125"></join>, three metal bells, value 5 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18050424-22-victim272" type="victimName">
                  Thomas 
                  Mears
